{"article_id":"fj5ur3GxVy8ilCWH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The possible shift ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"first reported by The Washington Post on Tuesday ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"came days after the United States disclosed its preliminary intelligence assessment","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"that chemical munitions ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"which Mr. Assad ' s military has been known to stockpile ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"had been used on a small scale in Syria .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Obama ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"who has said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the use of these weapons would be a \" game changer , \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"has also said","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"before responding ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he needs more conclusive proof","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that Mr. Assad had deployed these weapons","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"- a point","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he re-emphasized at a wide-ranging news conference in Washington earlier Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"\" What we now have is evidence","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that chemical weapons have been used inside of Syria ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"but we don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"how they were used , when they were used ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who used them ;","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"we don ' t have chain of custody","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that establishes what exactly happened , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"\" And when I am making decisions about America ' s national security and the potential","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"for taking additional action in response to chemical weapon use ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"I ' ve got to make sure","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"I ' ve got the facts . \"","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Mr. Obama also said","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" if we end up rushing to judgment","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"without hard , effective evidence ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"then we can find ourselves in the position","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"where we can ' t mobilize the international community","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to support what we do . \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"even without conclusive proof of chemical weapons use ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"officials said ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"the Pentagon has prepared a menu of options for Mr. Obama","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"that range from airstrikes and commando raids to the enforcement of a no-fly zone over Syria .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Officials said","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"the administration was also looking for ways","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"to increase its aid to the rebels .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Obama had long resisted calls","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to arm the rebels ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"including from David H. Petraeus , the former director of the Central Intelligence Agency , and former Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"A proposal by Mr. Petraeus","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to provide arms to carefully vetted members of the opposition","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"was shelved last fall ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"though several officials said","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"they expected it to be revisited .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":101,"left":56,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":56,"left":52,"right":55,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":2,"right":54,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":53,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":53,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":84,"right":99,"relation":"elabora